<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Url Shortener</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Url Shortener</h2>
    <p>
        This simple web app supports:
        <ol>
            <li>Account creation</li>
            <li>URL registration to get short URL</li>
            <li>URL statistics per account</li>
            <li>Redirection to target URL when hitting a short URL</li>
        </ol>
    </p>
    <p>
        Detailed <a href="swagger-ui.html"> REST-endpoints documentation</a> is available via Swagger
    </p>

    <p>
        You can run the app
        <ul>
            <li>from IntellJ IDEA: there is UrlShortener run configuration shared, Tomcat integration is required</li>
            <li>from Tomcat: need to deploy the generated war file manually</li>
        </ul>
    </p>

</body>
</html>